WEBVTT

00:00.499 --> 00:01.166
(MUSIC PLAYING)

00:03.915 --> 00:05.208
So beautiful...

00:05.208 --> 00:06.457
But we're not gonna
get that ship

00:06.457 --> 00:07.666
by just dreaming about it.

00:07.666 --> 00:09.000
Enough bottom feeding, Groot.

00:09.000 --> 00:10.666
We gotta start aiming
for the top.

00:10.666 --> 00:12.707
Bounty on this guy
is 500,000 credits.

00:12.707 --> 00:14.707
That new ship will be mine.
I am Groot...

00:15.749 --> 00:17.000
(CLASSICAL MUSIC PLAYING)

00:18.000 --> 00:19.457
ROCKET: All right.

00:19.457 --> 00:21.166
Get in the restaurant,
nab this alien

00:21.166 --> 00:22.790
without any fuss,
and be on our way.

00:22.790 --> 00:24.624
(CLEARS THROAT)

00:24.624 --> 00:26.166
Hey, we got somebody
to meet in there.

00:26.166 --> 00:27.624
I am Groot.

00:27.624 --> 00:29.374
I could never permit someone

00:29.374 --> 00:31.208
with such horrid
personal hygiene

00:31.208 --> 00:32.374
to enter

00:32.374 --> 00:34.291
this establishment.

00:34.291 --> 00:36.416
I haven't taken
a shower in six years

00:36.416 --> 00:38.374
and I ain't
about to start now.

00:38.374 --> 00:41.499
(GRUNTS) I'll show you some
personal hygiene,
you stuffed shirt...

00:42.166 --> 00:43.457
Groot, put me down.

00:45.166 --> 00:47.208
No way. I am not
getting in there.

00:47.208 --> 00:48.707
Hey! Hey! (EXCLAIMS)

00:48.707 --> 00:49.790
Stop it!

00:49.790 --> 00:50.874
(GRUNTING)

00:50.874 --> 00:52.457
Don't touch me!

00:52.457 --> 00:53.457
(ROCKET GRUNTING)

00:54.457 --> 00:55.832
Not getting in there!

00:57.000 --> 00:58.000
(WATER SPLASHING)

01:01.707 --> 01:04.707
I cleaned up to get
into your stupid restaurant.

01:04.707 --> 01:05.915
(CLENCHING TEETH)
Let us in.

01:05.915 --> 01:08.416
I was not speaking
of your hygiene.

01:08.416 --> 01:10.249
I was referring to his.

01:10.249 --> 01:11.541
I am Groot.

01:11.541 --> 01:15.541
Imagine, an unpruned topiary
in this establishment.

01:15.541 --> 01:17.416
Not now, not ever.

01:18.374 --> 01:19.915
(CHUCKLES)
I am Groot.

01:19.915 --> 01:21.000
(GROWLING)

01:21.915 --> 01:23.374
I am Groot.

01:24.374 --> 01:25.957
Oh, I'll tell you
(SAW WHIRRING)

01:25.957 --> 01:27.416
when it's short enough.

01:27.416 --> 01:28.915
(LAUGHING EVILLY)
I am Groot!
